figlet is a tool that can be used to format the text on screen
for example
figlet wick will display


                            __      _(_) ___| | __
                           \ \ /\ / / |/ __| |/ /
                            \ V  V /| | (__|   < 
                            \_/\_/  |_|\___|_|\_\ 


to install it in linux use
apt-get install figlet
